  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/909dd719e779b7038ea6b4467d16633d.avif?t=1773922450\" width=640 height=613 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>A tale of Struggle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>\"..destiny won't stay idle as we fight it..\"</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>  </strong>      <br><strong>\"When a Mortal defeats the Aeon of Death,  </strong><br><strong>It's rewarded with Eternal Life\"  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>..to claim the prize for themselves,   humanity challenged Death..</strong>   <br><strong>..but Defeat shattered their dreams of Glory.</strong>.   <br><strong>..and Despair sat on the throne of Hope..</strong>   <br><strong>..as the Aeon's might was beyond their reach..</strong>   <br><strong>..a curse was cast upon them.. </strong>     <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/819e91a7416b884bea60b9990e854a70.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/819e91a7416b884bea60b9990e854a70.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/819e91a7416b884bea60b9990e854a70.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow the story of the nine protagonists in a cursed world with only seven days left. Witness the events from their point of view as the road to salvation is threatened by dark forces and each protagonist has a crucial role to play. With the chosen entering the Tower of Guardiah, a knight seeking hope, a mage looking for answers and the monsters rebelling to humanity, the story will keep you engaged till the very end.    </strong>   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Gameplay <br>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/6deb6cc5a1db27ba2cdc5e2fb9e1588a.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/6deb6cc5a1db27ba2cdc5e2fb9e1588a.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/6deb6cc5a1db27ba2cdc5e2fb9e1588a.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Each protagonist has its own fighting style, from stealthy thieves to knights and mages, you will play as both humans and monsters. The field action is different in each level to keep your playthrough always fresh.  <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/4b303c6e4db7927451b3a1fbf6a40e5b.avif?t=1773922450\" width=616 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Among the heroes Roy and Eria are of a special kind. not only you can switch between them at will but they can also save each other if their beloved is in danger !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Turn Based !<br>   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/880320276fcde001d33909303905d37d.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/880320276fcde001d33909303905d37d.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/880320276fcde001d33909303905d37d.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To complement the field action there is a fast paced turn based combat that lets you quickly send your fighters in battle, use <u>Magic and the powerful \"Fireburn\" abilities</u>. You can also  take your time to craft a winning strategy by reading the battle notes filled with your enemies' skills and weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/ec27c7aa7ecb8da67f8e8dec4bd73296.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/ec27c7aa7ecb8da67f8e8dec4bd73296.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/ec27c7aa7ecb8da67f8e8dec4bd73296.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the field action relies only on your skills and your ability to run, kite and strike, your party will become stronger  as the story progresses. With new Spells,  Fireburns and new party members that will  join your fight.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Tactical combat out of bounds !</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/26f6d6ebecfb840f75cf92c02512926c.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/26f6d6ebecfb840f75cf92c02512926c.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/26f6d6ebecfb840f75cf92c02512926c.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One of the tactical aspects of the game comes for the close interaction between field action and turn based combat, each one with the power to influence the other making you <u>think outside the box to craft a winning strategy</u>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can heal your party HP while on the field by defeating enemies, enter optional battles to gain a magic charge and <u>use souls as party members</u>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the turn based combat starts, the action on the field is frozen so even if you are one step away from death you can unleash your Fireburn in battle to gain one life and burn nearby enemies when the action is restored !     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Lore and fun <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/469a5e1450df8fe23ee243f89b6256be.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/469a5e1450df8fe23ee243f89b6256be.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/469a5e1450df8fe23ee243f89b6256be.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the guilty pleasure of Skipping Cutscenes to see what happens..  the game offers twice the story at the same price ! And while exploring you will find many books that will allow you to expand your knowledge, while not mandatory, there's plenty of Lore if you want to better understand the events of the world.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Ten bad Fates<br>    <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/b0359fb9577b315a00852a7ac8bc76e5.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/b0359fb9577b315a00852a7ac8bc76e5.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/b0359fb9577b315a00852a7ac8bc76e5.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ten bad fates</strong> are there for you to discover while screwing up with many ways to die and unexpected ways to lose !<br> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>An Outstanding Soundtrack </strong><br>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/7ed0d206c24bad10b7b859de576dcead.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/7ed0d206c24bad10b7b859de576dcead.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/7ed0d206c24bad10b7b859de576dcead.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> A fantastic soundtrack for an epic story, Fate of Fire boasts 42 tracks composed by the amazing <strong>Tim Beek</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Made with Love, with LÖVE<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/dd1291f68fc9fae7ff68e6734afeb04f.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made with the fantastic LÖVE 2d framework, Fate of Fire is a work of love and passion. Over time, update after update it became better and better as I have always been working on the game to make it awesome !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">The Demo<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <br>A lengthy demo to introduce you to the story and let you taste the game playing with five of the main characters. The demo is always updated with the latest features and your progress will be loaded in the full version. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Have fun Saving Humanity !   </strong>     <br><strong>Denis ^^</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/46828791b955e88ee55d3b38463e7a46.avif?t=1773922450\" width=74 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/909dd719e779b7038ea6b4467d16633d.avif?t=1773922450\" width=640 height=613 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>A tale of Struggle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>\"..destiny won't stay idle as we fight it..\"</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>  </strong>      <br><strong>\"When a Mortal defeats the Aeon of Death,  </strong><br><strong>It's rewarded with Eternal Life\"  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>..to claim the prize for themselves,   humanity challenged Death..</strong>   <br><strong>..but Defeat shattered their dreams of Glory.</strong>.   <br><strong>..and Despair sat on the throne of Hope..</strong>   <br><strong>..as the Aeon's might was beyond their reach..</strong>   <br><strong>..a curse was cast upon them.. </strong>     <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/819e91a7416b884bea60b9990e854a70.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/819e91a7416b884bea60b9990e854a70.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/819e91a7416b884bea60b9990e854a70.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow the story of the nine protagonists in a cursed world with only seven days left. Witness the events from their point of view as the road to salvation is threatened by dark forces and each protagonist has a crucial role to play. With the chosen entering the Tower of Guardiah, a knight seeking hope, a mage looking for answers and the monsters rebelling to humanity, the story will keep you engaged till the very end.    </strong>   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Gameplay <br>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/6deb6cc5a1db27ba2cdc5e2fb9e1588a.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/6deb6cc5a1db27ba2cdc5e2fb9e1588a.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/6deb6cc5a1db27ba2cdc5e2fb9e1588a.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Each protagonist has its own fighting style, from stealthy thieves to knights and mages, you will play as both humans and monsters. The field action is different in each level to keep your playthrough always fresh.  <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/4b303c6e4db7927451b3a1fbf6a40e5b.avif?t=1773922450\" width=616 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Among the heroes Roy and Eria are of a special kind. not only you can switch between them at will but they can also save each other if their beloved is in danger !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Turn Based !<br>   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/880320276fcde001d33909303905d37d.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/880320276fcde001d33909303905d37d.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/880320276fcde001d33909303905d37d.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To complement the field action there is a fast paced turn based combat that lets you quickly send your fighters in battle, use <u>Magic and the powerful \"Fireburn\" abilities</u>. You can also  take your time to craft a winning strategy by reading the battle notes filled with your enemies' skills and weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/ec27c7aa7ecb8da67f8e8dec4bd73296.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/ec27c7aa7ecb8da67f8e8dec4bd73296.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/ec27c7aa7ecb8da67f8e8dec4bd73296.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the field action relies only on your skills and your ability to run, kite and strike, your party will become stronger  as the story progresses. With new Spells,  Fireburns and new party members that will  join your fight.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Tactical combat out of bounds !</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/26f6d6ebecfb840f75cf92c02512926c.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/26f6d6ebecfb840f75cf92c02512926c.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/26f6d6ebecfb840f75cf92c02512926c.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One of the tactical aspects of the game comes for the close interaction between field action and turn based combat, each one with the power to influence the other making you <u>think outside the box to craft a winning strategy</u>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can heal your party HP while on the field by defeating enemies, enter optional battles to gain a magic charge and <u>use souls as party members</u>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the turn based combat starts, the action on the field is frozen so even if you are one step away from death you can unleash your Fireburn in battle to gain one life and burn nearby enemies when the action is restored !     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Lore and fun <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/469a5e1450df8fe23ee243f89b6256be.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/469a5e1450df8fe23ee243f89b6256be.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/469a5e1450df8fe23ee243f89b6256be.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the guilty pleasure of Skipping Cutscenes to see what happens..  the game offers twice the story at the same price ! And while exploring you will find many books that will allow you to expand your knowledge, while not mandatory, there's plenty of Lore if you want to better understand the events of the world.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Ten bad Fates<br>    <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/b0359fb9577b315a00852a7ac8bc76e5.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/b0359fb9577b315a00852a7ac8bc76e5.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/b0359fb9577b315a00852a7ac8bc76e5.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ten bad fates</strong> are there for you to discover while screwing up with many ways to die and unexpected ways to lose !<br> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>An Outstanding Soundtrack </strong><br>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/7ed0d206c24bad10b7b859de576dcead.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/7ed0d206c24bad10b7b859de576dcead.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/7ed0d206c24bad10b7b859de576dcead.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> A fantastic soundtrack for an epic story, Fate of Fire boasts 42 tracks composed by the amazing <strong>Tim Beek</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Made with Love, with LÖVE<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/dd1291f68fc9fae7ff68e6734afeb04f.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made with the fantastic LÖVE 2d framework, Fate of Fire is a work of love and passion. Over time, update after update it became better and better as I have always been working on the game to make it awesome !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">The Demo<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.poster.avif?t=1773922450\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.webm?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.mp4?t=1773922450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <br>A lengthy demo to introduce you to the story and let you taste the game playing with five of the main characters. The demo is always updated with the latest features and your progress will be loaded in the full version. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Have fun Saving Humanity !   </strong>     <br><strong>Denis ^^</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085800/extras/46828791b955e88ee55d3b38463e7a46.avif?t=1773922450\" width=74 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
